    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >体验版说明</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>在体验版中可以进行总共4个关卡，进度会延续到完整版！</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Description:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >成为幻想世界的英雄，阻止怪物入侵！<strong>《</strong>防御遗产<strong>》</strong>结合了创新的横向卷轴动作和卡牌构建元素。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >踏上冒险之旅，招募盟友，保护自己免受危险敌人的伤害！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3280850/extras/dcce87a67bc42555a09b99c41fa8a985.poster.avif?t=1765314227\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3280850/extras/dcce87a67bc42555a09b99c41fa8a985.webm?t=1765314227\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3280850/extras/dcce87a67bc42555a09b99c41fa8a985.mp4?t=1765314227\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>横向卷轴动作：体验以惊人的2D画面和直观的控制进行的激烈战斗。感受抵御成群怪物的刺激。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >卡牌构建策略：收集各种卡牌来创建你独特的卡组。每张卡牌都包含强大的技能，需要战略性的游戏玩法。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >幻想怪物：面对各种你只能想象的幻想怪物。与拥有不同能力的怪物战斗。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3280850/extras/28a868d1f6f5b6a21c0fef67ebe5a40e.poster.avif?t=1765314227\" width=600 height=298 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3280850/extras/28a868d1f6f5b6a21c0fef67ebe5a40e.webm?t=1765314227\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3280850/extras/28a868d1f6f5b6a21c0fef67ebe5a40e.mp4?t=1765314227\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>技能升级：通过战斗获取经验并升级英雄的技能。使用强大的技能有效清除怪物。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3280850/extras/9c7e4fa42764a857fee9606d893315ad.poster.avif?t=1765314227\" width=600 height=298 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3280850/extras/9c7e4fa42764a857fee9606d893315ad.webm?t=1765314227\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3280850/extras/9c7e4fa42764a857fee9606d893315ad.mp4?t=1765314227\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>防御源源不断的怪物。选择卡牌，使用技能击败敌人。战略性卡牌构建是胜利的关键。清除每个关卡，面对越来越强大的怪物，最终击败终极Boss！</p>",
